I only want to be married to Sad Yogi and only to Alan.

6
00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:31.880
So because we have learned many lessons of the past

7
00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:36.480
and the marriage has evolved and we found out things about each other,

8
00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:40.200
especially about ourselves through the process,

9
